headline: ICE Announces Its Treasury Clearing Application and Rulebook Have been Published by the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission
summary: ATLANTA & NEW YORK, August 19, 2025--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE: ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, today announced that the application and rulebook of ICE Clear Credit to expand its current registered clearing agency designation to add U.S. Treasury clearing has been published by the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC). headline: Xactus Achieves ICE Platinum Partner Status
summary: Xactus, a fintech and market leader in verification solutions for the mortgage industry, today announced it has been named an ICE Platinum Partner, a designation that signifies a high level of dedication, expertise, and engagement with ICE Mortgage Technology, part of Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE: ICE), a leading global provider of data, technology and market infrastructure.
